Entry.JapaneseText: この強さが あなたがたの生きてきた証
Entry.EnglishText: This strength is the proof you are alive.

Entry.JapaneseText: 過ちを受け止めた あなたがたの覚悟、 見せてもらいました
Entry.EnglishText: I can witness your resolution to undo your wrongs.

Entry.JapaneseText: これで私の役目は終わりです。 さようなら……
Entry.EnglishText: With this...my duty is finished. Farewell...

Entry.JapaneseText: エトくんは 無事みたいだね
……<CLE>さんたち、 こんなとこまでついて きてくれて……あんがと
Entry.EnglishText: ...You guys came all the way here for us. Thanks.

Entry.JapaneseText: いいや…… ここまで君たちと一緒に 旅ができてよかったよ
Entry.EnglishText: No, the one that should be glad is me. I'm happy I could journey with you.

Entry.JapaneseText: デリス・カーラーンで 何があったか…… それを知ることができましたし……
Entry.EnglishText: We could also learn the truth of what happened to Derris Kharlan...

Entry.JapaneseText: うん……それに君たちが いてくれたから、<CLE>や<MIN>、 <KLA>もこうして生きてる
Entry.EnglishText: Yeah...And thanks to you guys <CLE>, <MIN>, <CST> and everyone is alive and well!
W-what do you mean by that?

Entry.JapaneseText: え？ あ、気にしない、 気にしない
Entry.EnglishText: Oh, that? Don't worry, don't worry!

Entry.JapaneseText: でも……ここで…… こんな形でお別れなんてさ……
Entry.EnglishText: Still...this is...this is a sad way to part.

Entry.JapaneseText: だが、これが、君たちの決意なら 否定はしない
Entry.EnglishText: This is their decision, though. And if they are resolved I will support them.

Entry.JapaneseText: 私、忘れません、 あなたたちという 友達がいたことを……
Entry.EnglishText: I shall never forget about you. After all we are friends...

Entry.JapaneseText: 僕だって、 いや、みんなも 君たちの友達だ
Entry.EnglishText: Me too. Everyone here are your friends.

Entry.JapaneseText: ふたりとも…… 消えかけて……
もうお別れって ことみたいだぜ
Entry.EnglishText: It looks like it's time to say goodbye.

Entry.JapaneseText: ゴメンね、エト…… エトをひとり置き去りに していくみたいになって
Entry.EnglishText: I'm sorry, Eto...It's selfish of us to leave you all alone.

Entry.JapaneseText: いやだよ……行かないで…… ずっと一緒に楽しく……
Entry.EnglishText: No...don't go... There is so much to enjoy together...

Entry.JapaneseText: なんだよ〜、オレらの 決断受け止めるって 言ったじゃねーか！
Entry.EnglishText: Hey! You said you wouldn't try to stop us before!

Entry.JapaneseText: わたしも……もっともっと、 エトと思い出作りたかったよ
Entry.EnglishText: I...also wanted to create many, many memories together...

Entry.JapaneseText: こんなとこで、 お別れなんてイヤだよ……
Entry.EnglishText: I don't want to say goodbye just yet...!!

Entry.JapaneseText: ……なんだよ…… 決めたんだろ！
楽しかったよ、エト。 たくさんたくさん…… 思い出ありがと
Entry.EnglishText: It was fun, Eto. Thank you for all you've done for us...and all the memories...

Entry.JapaneseText: ……最後の、最後に…… ツライ想いさせてゴメンな
Entry.EnglishText: ...Sorry that we had to make the very last moments sad...

Entry.JapaneseText: オレってやっぱ 親不孝もんかも
Entry.EnglishText: We really are bad kids, huh?

Entry.JapaneseText: ぼくのかわいい双子だもん、 いい子じゃないはずが ないでしょ
Entry.EnglishText: You are my fair pair of twins. You will always be nothing but good kids.

Entry.JapaneseText: ……でも、 これきりだなんて……
Entry.EnglishText: But...this can't be where it ends...

Entry.JapaneseText: これきりじゃないよ、エト
Entry.EnglishText: This isn't the end yet, Eto.

Entry.JapaneseText: 全然大丈夫だって。 また会える
Entry.EnglishText: It's no problem at all! We'll meet again.

Entry.JapaneseText: 何言ってんの…… きみたちは……もう……
Entry.EnglishText: What are you saying...you are already...

Entry.JapaneseText: ううん…… ……そうだよ。 きっと、そう
Entry.EnglishText: No, I really do believe it...I'm sure...

Entry.JapaneseText: いつかって いつだよーっ！
